Class NetworkKeyManager

java.lang.Object

Direct Known Subclasses:
RepositoryKeyManager
public class NetworkKeyManager
extends BasicKeyManager

This is a network-based implementation of key manager. In comparison with BasicKeyManager, this class reads (or writes) the user's private key (as a java keystore) from (or to) NDN.

See Also:
BasicKeyManager, KeyManager
